Class MyHealthData

  • java.lang.Object
    • MyHealthData
  • class MyHealthData
extends Object
    This class takes the input and does various calculations on the input and display the health record of the patient The constructor of this class takes all the entered input into parameters. Then it sets the values of the variables. Various methods calculate the BMI,age,maximum and minimum targeted heart rate. Finally, displayMyHealthData displays all the health record of the patient.
